<%=@event.host_name%>&nbsp&nbsp<br>

<strong>Contact Organizer:</strong> 
<%=@event.cellnum%>&nbsp&nbsp<%=@user.email%><br>

<strong>People Attending:</strong> 
<%=@event.attending%><br>

<strong>People Reserved:</strong> 
<%=@event.reserved%>
